name: Cowboy Love is Pure 1-016: Couldn't
description: Chapter 1, panel 16. A cowboy must admit failure when it is plain to see. The pain will be great but a cowboy's endurance is a worthy tool. A rival may shuffle in to occupy the gaps in a cowboy's attention. The house lights rise, the bar reeks of sour beer. A comic by Little Old Man. This panel is an edition of 30.
